01:01:19,575 --> 01:01:23,022
You okay?

1065
01:01:29,852 --> 01:01:32,230
You've gotta be careful,

1066
01:01:32,288 --> 01:01:34,928
that truck must have been
going at least ninety.

1067
01:01:36,993 --> 01:01:40,634
Okay, "stay tuned"...
be alert in case of danger.

1068
01:01:40,697 --> 01:01:43,109
Ak for yourself...
make up your own mind.

1069
01:01:43,166 --> 01:01:44,440
Be an independent thinker.

1070
01:01:44,500 --> 01:01:46,138
Next,

1071
01:01:46,202 --> 01:01:47,806
I'm an eagle.

1072
01:01:47,870 --> 01:01:50,282
That just feel good to say it.

1073
01:01:50,339 --> 01:01:52,285
I'm an eagle.

1074
01:01:52,341 --> 01:01:54,548
Yeah, feels good.

1075
01:01:54,610 --> 01:01:58,251
I like to say "I'm a
Tyrannosaurus Rex."

1076
01:01:59,248 --> 01:02:01,990
come on, try it with me.

1077
01:02:02,051 --> 01:02:04,531
Uh-oh, work.

1078
01:02:09,225 --> 01:02:11,899
Stay here.

1079
01:02:11,961 --> 01:02:14,100
What seems to be the problem?

1080
01:02:14,163 --> 01:02:19,738
[speaking spanish]

1081
01:02:47,563 --> 01:02:50,271
I couldn't fix
my car if I had to.

1082
01:02:50,333 --> 01:02:53,974
The internal combustion engine
is all cause and effect.

1083
01:02:54,036 --> 01:02:56,812
Anyone can understand
it, then fix it.

1084
01:02:56,873 --> 01:02:58,875
As opposed to people?

1085
01:02:58,941 --> 01:03:00,921
Well, they're
not so easy to fix.

1086
01:03:00,977 --> 01:03:02,979
What is that supposed to mean?

1087
01:03:03,045 --> 01:03:10,588
Relationships... they don't last,
they all break in the end.

1088
01:03:10,653 --> 01:03:12,394
That's fairly pessimistic.

1089
01:03:12,455 --> 01:03:14,196
I'm being honest.

1090
01:03:14,257 --> 01:03:18,000
