of temporary friendships.

1093
01:03:26,135 --> 01:03:28,376
Then you move on.

1094
01:03:28,437 --> 01:03:31,577
I have friends and family
all over the country.

1095
01:03:31,641 --> 01:03:33,587
What about you?

1096
01:03:33,643 --> 01:03:35,953
Have you ever crossed
the state line?

1097
01:03:36,012 --> 01:03:40,859
It's not like I've
got family to visit.

1098
01:03:40,917 --> 01:03:45,991
Ok. I was engaged once,
but he wouldn't set a date.

1099
01:03:46,055 --> 01:03:49,366
Then I found out he
was already married.

1100
01:03:49,425 --> 01:03:53,305
No one else ever came close.

1101
01:03:53,362 --> 01:03:59,176
Maybe they don't all last
Lyman, but like they say,

1102
01:03:59,235 --> 01:04:02,773
doesn't mean the fall
wasn't worth the ride.

1103
01:04:09,111 --> 01:04:14,493
You know, you could pick
your own first name.

1104
01:04:14,550 --> 01:04:17,963
I never found a name
that seemed right.

1105
01:04:18,020 --> 01:04:21,024
I guess my mom wasn't one for
sewing on name-tags.

1106
01:04:21,090 --> 01:04:23,696
But what about your birthday?

1107
01:04:23,759 --> 01:04:25,534
When do you have your party?

1108
01:04:25,595 --> 01:04:29,236
It's not important.

1109
01:04:32,869 --> 01:04:34,746
FIONA: take this exit.

1110
01:04:34,804 --> 01:04:36,374
Make a right.

1111
01:04:36,439 --> 01:04:41,081
I want to show you something.

1112
01:04:41,143 --> 01:04:46,889
Your parents checked in here.
No previous address.

1113
01:04:46,949 --> 01:04:52,797
And then in a moment, they were
taken, and you continued.

1114
01:04:52,855 --> 01:04:55,267
After the accident, they
couldn't be traced.

1115
01:04:55,324 --> 01:05:00,672
No next-of-kin, and you
couldn't remember anything.

1116
01:05:00,730 --> 01:05:03,176
Missing persons
turned up nothing.

1117
01:05:03,232 --> 01:05:05,940
I chased every lead,
blood types,

1118
01:05:06,002 --> 01:05:10,144
car registration,
every receipt.

1119
01:05:10,206 --> 01:05:11,981
I just kept thinking that there
must have been somebody

1120
01:05:12,041 --> 01:05:15,318
out there who would
have missed them.

1121
01:05:19,248 --> 01:05:22,752
Code of the west, rule number
one, "don't inquire into a man's"

1122
01:05:22,818 --> 01:05:26,493
"past." don't you read those
books you pass around?

1123
01:05:26,555 --> 01:05:29,229
Rule number two,

1124
01:05:29,292 --> 01:05:34,469
"take the measure of a man
for what he is today."

1125
01:05:34,530 --> 01:05:38,501
you're right. I'm sorry.

1126
01:05:38,567 --> 01:05:42,208
Do you hate my guts now?

1127
