Does he still say
<i>"Hi-ho silver away?"</i>

1258
01:15:23,886 --> 01:15:25,160
No.

1259
01:15:25,220 --> 01:15:28,167
Oh.

1260
01:15:28,223 --> 01:15:30,396
I thought he was the smartest,
funniest thing in the world.

1261
01:15:30,459 --> 01:15:33,463
That was before
he met me, of course.

1262
01:15:33,529 --> 01:15:35,372
I was an only child.

1263
01:15:35,430 --> 01:15:37,569
This bird got me a lot of
friends at school.

1264
01:15:37,633 --> 01:15:41,240
He could do tricks, he was
like a one man circus.

1265
01:15:41,303 --> 01:15:45,479
Why did you sell
him, Mr. Weber?

1266
01:15:45,541 --> 01:15:48,488
Because I didn't want
him around the children.

1267
01:15:48,544 --> 01:15:51,616
I thought they
carried diseases.

1268
01:15:51,680 --> 01:15:53,717
That's not why you
wanted him out, ella.

1269
01:15:53,782 --> 01:15:56,854
It was the green-eyed
monster, jealousy.

1270
01:15:56,919 --> 01:15:58,921
She loves me more
than life itself.

1271
01:15:58,987 --> 01:16:01,126
She couldn't bare to
share me with anyone.

1272
01:16:01,189 --> 01:16:04,102
Well if you can find anyone
who'll take you now,

1273
01:16:04,159 --> 01:16:06,469
they're welcome to you.

1274
01:16:06,528 --> 01:16:08,474
He must have been pretty
rare back then,

1275
01:16:08,530 --> 01:16:10,567
did he come from a pet store?

1276
01:16:10,632 --> 01:16:13,169
Oh no, from a
neighbor, mrs. Hall.

1277
01:16:13,235 --> 01:16:16,580
She had a son michael, back
then we called retarded.

1278
01:16:16,638 --> 01:16:18,379
Dad I told you,
you can't say that.

1279
01:16:18,440 --> 01:16:22,081
...challenged,
yes. Challenged.

1280
01:16:22,144 --> 01:16:27,457
The kid learned to
speak by mimicking the bird.

1281
01:16:27,516 --> 01:16:29,120
Do you know where
the halls got him?

1282
01:16:29,184 --> 01:16:30,754
Oh sorry no,

1283
01:16:30,819 --> 01:16:32,799
I never asked, and
they're long dead now.

1284
01:16:32,854 --> 01:16:34,026
[chirping]

1285
01:16:34,089 --> 01:16:35,261
Ma 17!

1286
01:16:35,324 --> 01:16:36,826
Ma 17!

