01:16:36,892 --> 01:16:38,701
Ma 17!

1288
01:16:38,760 --> 01:16:40,671
It must have been hard
giving him up, Mr. Weber.

1289
01:16:40,729 --> 01:16:46,680
Yeah, but look what I got in
exchange. A world of family.

1290
01:16:46,735 --> 01:16:50,547
The bird got me
through my childhood,

1291
01:16:50,606 --> 01:16:54,110
ella got me through
the rest of it.

1292
01:16:56,778 --> 01:16:59,281
Thanks for bringing
him by, son.

1293
01:16:59,348 --> 01:17:01,089
I hope you find what
you're looking for.

1294
01:17:02,284 --> 01:17:05,094
[siren blaring]

1295
01:17:07,623 --> 01:17:12,629
[dog howling]

1296
01:17:19,101 --> 01:17:20,478
[dog whimpering]

1297
01:17:36,251 --> 01:17:39,858
[air horn blaring]

