01:18:18,360 --> 01:18:20,306
190 here.

1303
01:18:20,362 --> 01:18:22,035
Mile marker 83.

1304
01:18:22,097 --> 01:18:23,542
Driver's out of his car.

1305
01:18:23,598 --> 01:18:25,305
He looks drunk.

1306
01:18:25,367 --> 01:18:27,074
Send the troopers.

1307
01:18:27,135 --> 01:18:30,344
RADIO: 190, roger.

1308
01:18:30,405 --> 01:18:33,511
Why'd he want you
to shoot his car?

1309
01:18:33,575 --> 01:18:35,248
He was tired of it.

1310
01:18:35,310 --> 01:18:38,723
Gee, I'm tired of my boss...

1311
01:18:42,084 --> 01:18:43,961
why do you work
the night shift?

1312
01:18:44,019 --> 01:18:46,693
Because my husband does too.

1313
01:18:46,755 --> 01:18:51,670
It's the only way we can be
together, have a life.

1314
01:18:51,727 --> 01:18:54,833
