too stark for me.

1353
01:21:01,122 --> 01:21:06,162
I felt like that dog was a
part of me or something.

1354
01:21:06,228 --> 01:21:08,469
But I can't think
of you out there,

1355
01:21:08,530 --> 01:21:09,975
