to a slow fella.

1394
01:24:01,503 --> 01:24:03,312
Mike hall.

1395
01:24:03,371 --> 01:24:05,874
Yes.

1396
01:24:05,940 --> 01:24:07,817
And I lost track from there.

1397
01:24:07,876 --> 01:24:09,355
He still says your phone
number from when you

1398
01:24:09,411 --> 01:24:10,788
lived on summit drive.

1399
01:24:10,845 --> 01:24:12,552
Ma17?

1400
01:24:12,614 --> 01:24:14,753
That was our phone number?

1401
01:24:14,816 --> 01:24:17,558
He's got a better
memory than I do.

1402
01:24:17,619 --> 01:24:18,962
Who's bird was he?

1403
01:24:19,020 --> 01:24:20,727
My father's.

1404
01:24:20,789 --> 01:24:23,963
He was killed in the war.

1405
01:24:24,025 --> 01:24:25,834
Was he a religious man?

1406
01:24:25,894 --> 01:24:28,340
I don't think so.

1407
01:24:28,396 --> 01:24:31,775
Mother gave him a
bible before he left.

1408
01:24:31,833 --> 01:24:35,110
Father said he might not read
it, but he would keep it in his

1409
01:24:35,170 --> 01:24:40,279
breast pocket to protect him
from a well-aimed bullet.

1410
01:24:40,341 --> 01:24:43,117
What he worshipped
was this country.

1411
01:24:43,178 --> 01:24:44,782
Then who taught him
the bible verse...

1412
01:24:44,846 --> 01:24:47,759
'a bird of the air
shall carry the word?'

1413
01:24:47,816 --> 01:24:50,057
why, he came to us saying that.

1414
01:24:50,118 --> 01:24:51,995
Do you know where
your father got him?

1415
01:24:52,053 --> 01:24:55,159
Mother said that he
bought Mr. Roosevelt

1416
01:24:55,223 --> 01:24:59,137
