were passing through.

1417
01:25:03,164 --> 01:25:07,135
What does it
matter Mr. Lyman?

1418
01:25:07,202 --> 01:25:12,709
I've gone as far as I can go.

1419
01:25:12,774 --> 01:25:16,847
I don't know where to go next.

1420
01:25:16,911 --> 01:25:22,327
You go forward, Mr. Lyman.

1421
01:25:22,383 --> 01:25:26,490
Forward.

1422
01:25:31,559 --> 01:25:36,633
